#

Cajun Black Bean Burger

35 min
$8.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Egg

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianHigh Protein

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

EasyQuickSpicy

Description

A spicy, flavorful black bean burger with a kick of Cajun seasoning, served with fresh toppings.

Ingredients

  • black beans: 1 can (15 oz)
  • breadcrumbs: 1/2 cup
  • egg: 1
  • cajun seasoning: 2 tsp
  • garlic powder: 1 tsp
  • onion powder: 1 tsp
  • green bell pepper: 1/2, finely chopped
  • olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • burger buns: 2
  • lettuce: 2 leaves
  • tomato: 1, sliced
